Ansible Inventory

We have added create a base ansible inventory with aliases named web1, web2 and web3 for three web servers.
We create a database servers named server4 to have an alias db1

# Inventory File

web1 ansible_host=server1.business.com
web2 ansible_host=server2.business.com
web3 ansible_host=server3.business.com
db1 ansible_host=server4.business.com
